# Next.js frontend

- Prefer the **Next.js App Router**, TypeScript `strict`, Tailwind + shadcn/ui per system design.
- Server state lives in **TanStack Query**; reserve **Zustand** for UI-only state (modals, filters, etc.).
- Keep `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` env exposure minimal—API base URLs and feature flags only.
- API calls should target the Spring Cloud Gateway base URL (env-configured) instead of bespoke service ports.
